### [**Sandeep Singh Thakur vs State of Madhya Pradesh 2025 INSC 1499 \- Rape By Promise To Marry \- Quashed As Parties Married**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/12/Sandeep-Singh-Thakur-vs-State-of-Madhya-Pradesh-2025-INSC-1499---Rape-By-Promise-To-Marry---Quashed-As-Parties-Married.pdf)

**Constitution of India \- Article 142 \-** SC quashed a rape case after noticing that the parties (accused and victim) have married and residing together.

