### [**Baburam Gautam vs State of U.P. 2025 INSC 1493 \- Irretrievable Breakdown Of Marriage**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/12/Baburam-Gautam---vs-State-of-U.P.-2025-INSC-1493---Irretrievable-Breakdown-Of-Marriage.pdf)

