### [**Chandrashekar C v. State of Karnataka 2025 INSC 1491 \- S.482 CrPC \- Quashing**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/12/Chandrashekar-C-v.-State-of-Karnataka--2025-INSC-1491---S.482-CrPC---Quashing.pdf)

**Code of Criminal Procedure \- Section 482 \-** HC refused to quash criminal proceedings- Allowing appeal, SC quashed the proceedings

 

 

