### [**A. Jyothi vs. ICICI Lombard General Insurance Company Area Manager 2025 INSC 1469 \- S.163A MV Act \- Negligence Of Insured \- Larger Bench Reference**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/12/A.-Jyothi--vs.-ICICI-Lombard-General-Insurance-Company-Area-Manager--2025-INSC-1469---S.163A-MV-Act---Negligence-Of-Insured---Larger-Bench-Reference.pdf)

**Motor Vehicles Act \- Section 163A \-** There is considerable difference of opinion with respect to whether Section 163A of the MV Act could be invoked in the case of such accidents caused by the negligence of the insured himself \- Appeal directed to be tagged along with Larger bench reference. (Para 4-5)  
 

