### [**Mool Chand v. State Govt. of NCT of Delhi 2025 INSC 1448 \- Quashing On Settlement**](https://www.caseciter.com/mool-chand-v-state-govt-of-nct-of-delhi-2025-insc-1448-quashing-on-settlement/#gsc.tab=0)

**Code of Criminal Procedure 1973 \- Section 482 \-** HC refused to quash criminal proceedings based on settlement \- Allowing appeal, SC observed; we find that there has been a settlement of the dispute which is essentially a civil dispute between the appellant and respondent. (Para 22\)

