### [**Maneeta Singh & Ors. v. Virendra Pratap Singh 2025 INSC 1438- Motor Accident Compensation \- Coolie**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/12/Maneeta-Singh---Ors.-v.-Virendra-Pratap-Singh--2025-INSC-1438--Motor-Accident-Compensation---Coolie.pdf)

**Motor Accident Compensation \-** While enhancing compensation, SC observed: an enhancement of Rs.500/- per year is reasonable even in the case of a Coolie which will take the income of a Coolie in the year 2008 in which the accident occurred to Rs.6,500/-. In the above circumstances, this Court finds it reasonable to adopt the income claimed by the appellants at Rs.7,000. (Para 4\)

