### [**Ashraf v. State of Karnataka; 2025 INSC 1394- S.304A IPC**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/12/Ashraf-v.-State-of-Karnataka--2025-INSC-1394--S.304A-IPC.pdf)

**Indian Penal Code 1860 \- Section 304A \-** Partly allowing appeal, Supreme Court converted punishment to one of imprisonment till the rising of the Court with a total fine of Rs.1,31,000.

