### [**Rani @ Raj Kumari & Ors v. Kamlakat Gupta 2025 INSC 1393 \-Motor Accident Compensation \- Multiplier \- Stone Crusher Employee**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/12/Rani-@-Raj-Kumari---Ors-v.-Kamlakat-Gupta--2025-INSC-1393--Motor-Accident-Compensation---Multiplier---Stone-Crusher-Employee.pdf)

**Motor Accident Compensation \-** When the deceased was in the age group of 30 to 35 years,, it would be proper to apply multiplier of 16.(Para 5.3) it is normal to expect that a person employed in this stone crusher unit would earn Rs. 6.000/- every month. (Para 5.1)

