### [**Pankaj Shukla v. Deepak Chaturvedi 2025 INSC 1312 \- Matrimonial**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/11/Pankaj-Shukla-v.-Deepak-Chaturvedi-2025-INSC-1312---Matrimonial.pdf)

**Constitution of India \- Article 142**\- Matrimonial Matters \-It would serve no purpose to perpetuate a legal relationship when the matrimonial ties have long ceased to exist in substance \- Divorce Decree upheld.

