### [**Riyas v. P. N. Shinosh 2025 INSC 1303 \- Motor Accident Compensation**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/11/Riyas-v.-P.-N.-Shinosh--2025-INSC-1303---Motor-Accident-Compensation.pdf)

**Motor Accident Compensation** \- Supreme Court allowed appeal and enhanced compensation.

