### [**Akula Narayana v. Oriental Insurance Company Limited 2025 INSC 1301 \- Motor Accident Compensation \- Pay & Recover**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/11/Akula-Narayana-v.---Oriental-Insurance-Company-Limited--2025-INSC-1301---Motor-Accident-Compensation---Pay---Recover.pdf)

**Motor Accident Compensation** \- Where the contract of insurance is not disputed, even on breach of insurance conditions, this Court had allowed recovery of compensation from the insurer by giving right to the insurer to recover the same from the vehicle owner6. The pay and recover principle has been consistently followed even though it was doubted in a reference which remained unanswered. (Para 12\)

