### [**M.C. Mehta v. Union of India 2025 INSC 1274**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/10/M.C.-Mehta-v.-Union-of-India-2025-INSC-1274-.pdf)

**Note:** No legal aspects discussed in the judgment

