### [**Atomberg Technologies Pvt. Ltd. vs. Eureka Forbes Ltd. 2025 INSC 1253 \- Patents Act \- Suit For Groundless Threat Of Infringement \- Suit For Infringement**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/10/Atomberg-Technologies-Pvt.-Ltd.-vs.-Eureka-Forbes-Ltd.---2025-INSC-1253---Patents-Act---Suit-For-Groundless-Threat-Of-Infringement---Suit-For-Infringement.pdf)

**Patents Act, 1970 \- Section 104, 106, 108 \-**suit for Groundless Threat of Infringement governed by Section 106 of the Patents Act, 1970, has an independent cause of action from that of a suit for infringement. (Para 9\)

