### [**Kachara Vahatuk Sharamik Sangh vs Ajoy Mehta 2025 INSC 1227 \- Contempt**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/10/Kachara-Vahatuk-Sharamik-Sangh-vs-Ajoy-Mehta---2025-INSC-1227---Gratuity-Act---Contempt.pdf)

**Note**: No legal aspects discussed in this judgment \- SC closed contempt petition  against the BMC while issuing final directions to ensure full compliance with its 07.04.2017 judgment on regularizing sanitation workers. 

