### [**Prakash Namdeorao Dhage V/S Ganpati Yadavrao Kumbhare Southern \+ Nagpur Co-operative Society Ltd. v. Ganpati Yadavrao Kumbhare 2025 INSC 1225/1226**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/10/Prakash-Namdeorao-Dhage-V-S-Ganpati--Yadavrao-Kumbhare-Southern---Nagpur-Co-operative-Society-Ltd.-v.-Ganpati-Yadavrao-Kumbhare--2025-INSC-1225-1226.pdf)

**Note**: No legal aspects discussed in this judgment 

