[**Usha Kiran Kshatri vs State of Telangana 2025 INSC 1169 \- Judicial Service**](https://lawlens.in/doc/fd9655b6-2796-5940-b9ab-80f5dedde989?ref=caseciter.com)

**Judicial Service** \- No legal aspects discussed in this judgment \[SC request the High Court to declare the results of the appellants/petitioners/intervenors and to proceed for verification of their credentials/antecedents. Such of the qualified appellants/petitioners/intervenors who are found suitable may be appointed by offering them letters of appointment, as a special case, as early as possible but not later than two months from date of service of a copy of this order on the High Court- This order is strictly confined to the facts and circumstances of the appeals and petitions before us and may not be treated as a precedent for future cases \]

