### [**Rajesh Kumar v. State of Jharkhand 2025 INSC 1146 \- Service Law**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/09/Rajesh-Kumar-v.-State-of-Jharkhand--2025-INSC-1146---Service-Law.pdf)

**Service Law \-** No legal aspects discussed in this judgment- Supreme Court quashes cancellation of appointment of the appellant and directs to reinstate him in the Government School forthwith.

