### [**High Court of Madhya Pradesh vs Jyotsna Dohalia 2025 INSC 1137 \- Judicial Service Exams**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/09/High-Court-of-Madhya-Pradesh-vs-Jyotsna-Dohalia--2025-INSC-1137---Judicial-Service-Exams.pdf)

