### [**Thammineni Bhaskar v. State of Andhra Pradesh 2025 INSC 1124 \- Concurrent Murder Conviction Set Aside**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/09/Thammineni-Bhaskar-v.-State-of-Andhra-Pradesh-2025-INSC-1124---Concurrent-Murder-Conviction-Set-Aside.pdf)

**Indian Penal Code 1860 \- Section 302 \-** Concurrent conviction of murder accused set aside- No legal aspects discussed in the judgment.

