### [**Kisan Vithoba Aakhade (D) vs. Suresh Tukaram Nerkar 2025 INSC 1092 \-Civil Suit- Possession**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/09/Kisan-Vithoba-Aakhade--D--vs.-Suresh-Tukaram-Nerkar-2025-INSC-1092--Civil-Suit--Possession.pdf)

**Civil Suit \- Possession \-** mere reason of the manure and waste having been found in the property, cannot lead to a finding of possession. (Para 10\)

