### [**Const. Amar Singh v. Union of India 2025 INSC 1055 \- CISF \- Disciplinary Proceedings**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/08/Const.-Amar-Singh-v.-Union-of-India-2025-INSC-1055---CISF---Disciplinary-Proceedings.pdf)

**Note**: No legal aspects discussed in this judgment \- Supreme Court upheld the disciplinary penalty against appellant for misconduct while serving in CISF.

