### [**R Raghu vs G M Krishna**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/08/R-Raghu-vs-G-M-Krishna-2025-INSC-1040---Auction-Sale.pdf) **[2025 INSC 1040 \- Auction Sale](https://www.caseciter.com/r-raghu-vs-g-m-krishna-2025-insc-1040-auction-sale/#gsc.tab=0)**

**Note**: No legal aspects discussed in this judgment \[Supreme Court upheld an auction sale of disputed land, requiring additional payment and a fresh survey\]  
