### [**Reetesh Kumar Singh vs State of Uttar Pradesh**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/08/Reetesh-Kumar-Singh-vs-State-of-Uttar-Pradesh--2025-INSC-1031.pdf) **[2025 INSC 1031](https://www.caseciter.com/reetesh-kumar-singh-vs-state-of-uttar-pradesh-2025-insc-1031/)**

