### [**Kavin v. P. Sreemani Devi**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/08/Kavin-v.-P.-Sreemani-Devi--2025-INSC-1028---Motor-Accident-Compensation--Permanent-Disability.pdf) **[2025 INSC 1028 \- Motor Accident Compensation \-Permanent Disability](https://www.caseciter.com/kavin-v-p-sreemani-devi-2025-insc-1028-motor-accident-compensation-permanent-disability/)**

**Motor Accident Compensation \-** The grant of compensation for loss of future income is a distinct head from the one under which compensation is granted for permanent disability \[**Context**: In this case, SC observed that as claimant suffered 100% permanent disability and was living in a vegetative state, the High Court was not justified in setting aside the grant of compensation under this permanent disability head.\]

