### [**Mathews J. Nedumpara vs Supreme Court of India**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/08/Mathews-J.-Nedumpara-vs-Supreme-Court-of-India---WP-Seeking-FIR-Dismissed---Burnt-Currency-Notes.pdf) **[2025 INSC 941 \- WP Seeking FIR Dismissed \- Burnt Currency Notes](https://www.caseciter.com/mathews-j-nedumpara-vs-supreme-court-of-india-2025-insc-941-wp-seeking-fir-dismissed-burnt-currency-notes/)**

