### [**Lokesh B vs Suryanarayana Raju Jaggiraju**](https://www.caseciter.com/content/files/2025/08/Lokesh-B-vs-Suryanarayana-Raju-Jaggiraju--2025-INSC-939---Motor-Accident-Compensation---Self-Employed-Claimant---Future-Prospects.pdf) **[2025 INSC 939 \- Motor Accident Compensation \- Self Employed Claimant \- Future Prospects](https://www.caseciter.com/lokesh-b-v-suryanarayana-raju-jaggiraju-anr-neutral-citation-2025-insc-939/)**

**Motor Accident Compensation**\- Even if claimant is self-employed, he/she is entitled to future prospects. (Para 7\)

