### [**Santhosh Karunakaran vs. Ombudsman cum Ethics Officer, Kerala Cricket Association 2025 INSC 906**](https://www.caseciter.com/santhosh-karunakaran-vs-ombudsman-cum-ethics-officer-kerala-cricket-association-2025-insc-906/)

**Note**: No legal aspects discussed in the judgment.

