### [**Metpalli Lasum Bai (D) vs Metapalli Muthaih(D) 2025 INSC 879 \- Will \- Presumption Regarding Genuineness**](https://www.caseciter.com/metpalli-lasum-bai-d-vs-metapalli-muthaih-d-2025-insc-879-will-presumption-regarding-genuineness/)

**Will**\- When the Will is a registered document,there is a presumption regarding genuineness thereof and the burden would lie on the party who disputed its existence. (Para 9\)

