### [**New India Assurance Vs Usha Devi 2025 INSC 836 \- Motor Accident Compensation Claims- S.163A MV Act \- Question Of Negligence**](https://www.caseciter.com/new-india-assurance-vs-usha-devi-2025-insc-motor-accident-compensation-claims-s-163a-mv-act-question-of-negligence/) 

**Motor Vehicles Act \- Section 163A** \- While entertaining a claim petition u/s 163A of the Act, the question of negligence cannot be looked into. (Para 11\)

