### [**Communidade of Tivim vs. State of Goa 2025 INSC 835 \-Code of Comunidades**](https://www.caseciter.com/communidade-of-tivim-vs-state-of-goa-2025-insc-835-code-of-comunidades/)

**Code of Comunidades-** Art. 30 (4) (g) of the Code merely empowers a Communidade to deliberate upon terms of compromise, which upon finalisation, has to be forwarded to the Administrative Tribunal. This does not mean that it confers an unfettered power on the Communidade to enter into a compromise, without the Tribunal’s sanction.  (Para 20\)  
 

