[**N. Eswaranathan vs State 2025 INSC 509- AoR \- Vexatious Petition**](https://www.caseciter.com/n-eswaranathan-vs-state-2025-insc-509-aor-vexatious-petition/)

**Summary**: Proceedings against AoR and Advocate for filing a second SLP when a SLP had already been dismissed- Divergent view on the issue of acceptance of the apology \- Referred to CJI.

