[**Pawan Kumar Agrawal vs State Of Chhattisgarh 2025 INSC 545**](https://www.caseciter.com/pawan-kumar-agrawal-vs-state-of-chhattisgarh-2025-insc-545/)

**Note**: No legal aspects discussed in this judgment.

