[**Rajan Chadha vs Sanjay Arora 2025 INSC 546 \- Contempt of Court**](https://www.caseciter.com/rajan-chadha-vs-sanjay-arora-2025-insc-546-contempt-of-court/)

**Contempt of Courts Act \-** When one Judge of the same Court has taken a particular view holding the Respondent to be guilty of contempt, another Judge could not have come to a finding that the Respondent was not guilty of contempt. (Para 19\)  
