### [**A.J. Shetty And Co. Pvt. Ltd. vs St. Antony’s Charity Institutes 2025 INSC 547**](https://www.caseciter.com/a-j-shetty-and-co-pvt-ltd-vs-st-antonys-charity-institutes-2025-insc-547/)

