[**Shrikanth NS vs K. Munivenkatappa 2025 INSC 557- Order XI Rule 14 CPC**](https://www.caseciter.com/shrikanth-ns-vs-k-munivenkatappa-2025-insc-557-order-xi-rule-14-cpc/)

**Code of Civil Procedure 1908 \- Order XI Rule 14 \-** The provision enables the Court to seek production of the documents during the pendency of the suit. (Para 9\)

