[**State Of Himachal Pradesh vs Sanjay Kumar 2025 INSC 561 \- Rape Case \- Acquittal**](https://www.caseciter.com/state-of-himachal-pradesh-vs-sanjay-kumar-2025-insc-561-rape-case-acquittal/)

**Summary**: SC upheld acquittal of accused in rape case and observed: there is material contradiction in the statement of the Prosecutrix as to the date of commission of rape.

