### [**Muppidi Lakshmi Narayana Reddy Vs State Of Andhra Pradesh 2025 INSC 562 \- S.498A IPC \- Dowry Prohibition Act**](https://www.caseciter.com/muppidi-lakshmi-narayana-reddy-vs-state-of-andhra-pradesh-2025/)

**Indian Penal Code 1860 \- Section 498A \- Dowry Prohibition Act** \- The practice of involving the relatives of the husband in dowry related matters deprecated \- Criminal case quashed.

