[**Jaipur Vidyut Vitaran Nigam Limited vs Rajasthan Textile Mills Association 2025 INSC 592 \- Electricity Act**](https://www.caseciter.com/jaipur-vidyut-vitaran-nigam-limited-vs-rajasthan-textile-mills-association-2025-insc-592-electricity-act/)

**Electricity Act 2003 \- Section 42 ; Rajasthan Tariff Regulations, 2014 \-** Neither in the provisions of the 2003 Act nor under the provisions of the Rajasthan Tariff Regulations, 2014, is there a provision which makes the determination of the CSS simultaneously with the determination of the tariff mandatory- the determination of CSS is not necessarily a part of the tariff determination process. (Para 15-19)

