### [**A.M. Kulshrestha vs Union Bank of India 2025 INSC 744 \- Disciplinary Proceedings Quashed**](https://www.caseciter.com/a-m-kulshrestha-vs-union-bank-of-india-2025-insc-744-disciplinary-proceedings-quashed/)

**Note**: No legal aspects discussed in the judgment \- SC quashed charge sheet served on bank employee pursuant to disciplinary proceedings .

